---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "How to Use AppliTrack";
---

<Layout title={title}>
    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">Getting Started</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">Zero-configuration setup. Just browse and apply.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 mb-24">
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
                <div class="text-secondary font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Step 01</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Browse & Apply</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Navigate to LinkedIn, Indeed, Glassdoor, or Internshala. AppliTrack's background script automatically detects when you click an <strong>"Apply"</strong> or <strong>"Easy Apply"</strong> button.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">
                    *Tip: It even works on search result pages!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#1E293B] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="w-3/4 bg-dark rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/5 shadow-2xl">
                    <div class="h-4 w-1/2 bg-white/20 rounded mb-4"></div>
                    <div class="h-10 w-32 bg-primary rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm cursor-pointer hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                        Easy Apply
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-1/3">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white drop-shadow-lg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 2l12 11.2-5.8.5 3.1 7.3-2 1-3.1-7.4-4.5 4V2z"/></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12 mb-24">
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
                <div class="text-primary font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Step 02</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Manage in Kanban</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Open the extension popup to see your new application in the <strong>"Applied"</strong> column. Drag and drop cards as you progress to "Interviewing" or "Offer".
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#1E293B] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="flex gap-2 w-full h-32">
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-dark/50 rounded border border-white/5 p-2">
                        <div class="w-full bg-card p-2 rounded mb-2 border-l-2 border-primary text-xs text-gray-400">Software Engineer</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-dark/50 rounded border border-white/5 p-2">
                        <div class="w-full h-full border-2 border-dashed border-gray-700 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-gray-600 text-xs">Drop Here</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-dark/50 rounded border border-white/5 p-2"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
                <div class="text-success font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Step 03</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Track & Follow Up</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Check the Analytics tab to see your stats. If an application sits in "Applied" for more than 7 days, the Reminders tab will generate a follow-up email draft for you.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 bg-[#1E293B] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">12</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pending Follow-ups</div>
                    <button class="mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-sm text-primary hover:text-white hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                        Draft Email
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
</Layout>